OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F442A1775495152
OL,3,CPaid bereavement leave for parents
OL,4,Ccomes in in Northern Ireland
OL,6,FNorthern Ireland is the first part of
OL,7,Fthe UK to introduce paid miscarriage
OL,8,Fleave to parents.
OL,10,FFrom Monday 6 April, for employees
OL,11,Fthere will be two weeks of statutory
OL,12,Fpaid leave specifically for
OL,13,Fmiscarriage, whether through
OL,14,Fsponaneous loss or medical
OL,15,Finterventions necessary for health
OL,16,Freasons. This also applies to a
OL,17,Fpartner.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G1/4
