OL,3,CPaid bereavement leave for parents
OL,4,Ccomes in in Northern Ireland
OL,6,FThe new Regulations make Parental
OL,7,FBereavement Leave and Pay a day-one
OL,8,Fright for workers, abolishing the
OL,9,Fqualifying period of 26 weeks of
OL,10,Fcontinuous employment.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G2/4
