CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F442A1775495152
OL,3,CPaid bereavement leave for parents
OL,4,Ccomes in in Northern Ireland
OL,6,FEconomy Minister Dr Caoimhe Archibald
OL,7,Fsaid:"Parents who suffer the loss of a
OL,8,Fchild should be treated with care and
OL,9,Fcompassion. These new rights allow
OL,10,Fwomen who experience miscarriage and
OL,11,Ftheir partner to take up to two weeks
OL,12,Fof paid leave to grieve and to support
OL,13,Feach other during a very difficult
OL,14,Ftime. I welcome the Assembly's
OL,15,Fapproval of these Regulations, which
OL,16,Fwill make a meaningful difference to
OL,17,Fmany women and families across the
OL,18,Fnorth."
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G3/4
