PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F442A1775495152
OL,3,CPaid bereavement leave for parents
OL,4,Ccomes in in Northern Ireland
OL,6,FThe two weeks of leave for a woman and
OL,7,Fher partner is paid at the statutory
OL,8,Flevel of just more than #194 per week,
OL,9,For 90% of weekly pay if that's lower.
OL,11,FIt is estimated that over 9000 people
OL,12,Fper year are affected by a
OL,13,Fmiscarriage, either experienced by
OL,14,Fthem or their partner.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G4/4
